OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777986670
OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FDrone and missile strikes by Iran
OL,8,Fagainst the United Arab Emirates have
OL,9,Fbeen condemned by the Prime Minister.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer demanded an end to
OL,12,Fthe escalation and urged Iran to
OL,13,Fengage "meaningfully" in talks to
OL,14,Fensure the current Middle East
OL,15,Fceasefire was maintained.
OL,26,@uD@HOUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
