OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777986670
OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FMeanwhile, a US military commander
OL,8,Fsaid American forces were helping
OL,9,Frestore the flow of international
OL,10,Fshipping while Iran was doing all it
OL,11,Fcould to "terrorise and threaten"
OL,12,Fvessels.
OL,14,FAdmiral Brad Cooper, who heads up
OL,15,Fcentral command, said his military had
OL,16,F"the clear advantage" with an
OL,17,F"enormous amount of capability and
OL,18,Ffirepower" in and around the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz.
OL,26,@sD@JOUsD@aO]xD@AOUxD@UO]yD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777986670
OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FHis comments came as the US said two
OL,8,FUS-flagged cargo ships passed through
OL,9,Fthe critical waterway as part of a
OL,10,Fpush by President Donald Trump to
OL,11,Freopen the maritime pinchpoint, over
OL,12,Fwhich Iran has imposed a stranglehold.
OL,14,FThe effective closure of the vital
OL,15,Fsupply line for oil and gas has
OL,16,Finflicted a global economic shock and
OL,17,Fsent energy prices soaring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777986670
OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FHowever, the move to restore the sea
OL,8,Froute and free some 2,000 vessels
OL,9,Fstranded in the stand-off has shaken
OL,10,Fthe fragile ceasefire in the region.
OL,12,FThe United Arab Emirates said it came
OL,13,Funder attack for the first time since
OL,14,Fthe truce took hold in early April.
OL,16,FAn Iranian drone strike triggered a
OL,17,Ffire at a key oil facility, while it
OL,18,Fwas reported two cargo vessels were on
OL,19,Ffire off the country's coast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777986670
OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe American military said it had
OL,8,Fdestroyed six Iranian small boats and
OL,9,Fintercepted cruise missiles and drones
OL,10,Ffired by Tehran.
OL,12,FSir Keir said: "The UK condemns the
OL,13,Fdrone and missile strikes targeting
OL,14,Fthe United Arab Emirates.
OL,16,F"As I set out during my visit to the
OL,17,Fregion last month, stability in the
OL,18,FGulf directly affects the UK.
OL,26,@tD@POUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777986670
OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,F"We stand in solidarity with the UAE
OL,8,Fand will continue to support the
OL,9,Fdefence of our partners in the Gulf.
OL,11,F"This escalation must cease. Iran
OL,12,Fneeds to engage meaningfully in
OL,13,Fnegotiations to ensure the ceasefire
OL,14,Fin the Middle East endures, and a long-
OL,15,Fterm diplomatic solution is achieved."
OL,17,FAdmiral Cooper said: "We have defeated
OL,18,Feach and every one of those threats
OL,19,Fthrough the clinical application of
OL,20,Fdefensive munitions."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@fO]yD@VOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777986670
OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FHe said rather than providing
OL,8,Ftraditional escorts to vessels the US
OL,9,Fhad put in place "a much broader
OL,10,Fdefensive package".
OL,12,FHe also pointed out a blockade of
OL,13,FIranian ports remained in place to
OL,14,Fprevent oil shipments.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Tehran has disputed US
OL,17,Fclaims it had sunk six of its vessels
OL,18,Fand again warned all shipping must
OL,19,Fhave its permission to transit the
OL,20,Fstrait.
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
