PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777986670
OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FMajor general Ali Abdollahi told state
OL,8,FTV: "We warn that any foreign military
OL,9,Fforce ` especially the aggressive US
OL,10,Fmilitary ` that intends to approach or
OL,11,Fenter the Strait of Hormuz will be
OL,12,Ftargeted."
OL,14,FDespite the continuing impasse in the
OL,15,FGulf and the threat of fresh
OL,16,Fhostilities, Mr Trump insisted it was
OL,17,F"working out very nicely".
OL,26,@pD@EOUtD@JO]yD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
