PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777986670
OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FSpeaking to small business leaders at
OL,8,Fthe White house, the US president
OL,9,Fagain insisted that Iran could not be
OL,10,Fallowed to develop a nuclear weapon.
OL,12,FHe said: "They have no navy, they have
OL,13,Fno air force, they have no anti-
OL,14,Faircraft equipment. They have no
OL,15,Fradar, they have no nothing."
OL,17,FMr Trump described it as a mini-war
OL,18,F"because that's all they are".
OL,26,@tD@JOUwD@]O]zD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
