OL,3,CIran strikes on UAE condemned by
OL,4,CStarmer amid US bid to open Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FReferring to the spike in oil prices,
OL,8,Fhe added: "I see it going down very
OL,9,Fsubstantially when this is over."
OL,11,FMr Trump said at the weekend he was
OL,12,Fconsidering a new Iranian proposal to
OL,13,Fend the war but expressed doubt it
OL,14,Fwould lead to a deal.
OL,26,@pD@KOUqD@aO]
